00:03:53,790 --> 00:03:55,070
Follow up!

39
00:04:24,390 --> 00:04:25,190
Your Majesty!

40
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,770
You only rode the horse

41
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,270
and didn’t say anything.

42
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:30,430
I am not as smart as Fuheng,

43
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:33,370
