I made a mistake.

46
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:46,830
I owe a person.

47
00:04:50,150 --> 00:04:51,230
Your Majesty,

48
00:04:51,590 --> 00:04:53,150
everyone makes mistakes.

49
00:04:54,350 --> 00:04:56,630
