50
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:57,550
No.

51
00:05:00,550 --> 00:05:01,590
This is a mistake

52
00:05:03,670 --> 00:05:05,350
I can never make up for.

53
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:07,070
Your Majesty,

54
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:08,800
we can't go back to the past.

55
00:05:09,430 --> 00:05:11,470
If it’s a mistake can’t be made up for,

56
00:05:11,470 --> 00:05:13,600
then you should try to forget about it.

57
00:05:18,670 --> 00:05:19,550
No.

58
00:05:22,590 --> 00:05:23,850
