was perhaps the best relief for her.

86
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,430
But to me,

87
00:07:15,110 --> 00:07:17,470
it's a scandal I must cover.

88
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:21,030
Now I see

89
00:07:21,590 --> 00:07:23,920
that it’s not her who was too sentimental,

90
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:29,110
it’s me who was too ruthless.

91
00:07:34,110 --> 00:07:34,830
Go ahead.

92
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:36,390
Stop.

93
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,080
Give me your tag.

94
00:07:42,470 --> 00:07:44,790
I am a eunuch from Imperial Hospital.

95
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:47,190
I was ordered to dispose of old medicines.

96
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:48,030
Open it.

97
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:48,909
Yes.

98
00:07:55,310 --> 00:07:57,590
These are all medicines damaged by insects.

99
00:07:57,590 --> 00:07:59,710
We were supposed to throw them all away.

100
00:07:59,710 --> 00:08:02,310
But Imperial Doctors don’t want to waste them.

101
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:04,470
So they asked me to deliver all these

102
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:07,310
to Chongwen Gate to sell at a discount

103
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:11,070
and use the money we make on daily expenditures of the Imperial Hospital.

104
00:08:11,070 --> 00:08:13,670
Officer, it’ll be sunset soon,

105
00:08:14,230 --> 00:08:16,190
I am in a rush to leave the palace.

106
00:08:16,710 --> 00:08:18,870
Please allow me to pass.

107
00:08:22,230 --> 00:08:23,310
Greetings to Your Majesty.

108
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:25,030
Hailancha, go check

109
00:08:31,990 --> 00:08:33,230
what’s in the sack.

110
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:48,870
Your Majesty,

111
00:08:49,190 --> 00:08:51,520
it's perfectly fine caterpillar fungus.

112
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,110
How dare you

113
00:08:54,710 --> 00:08:56,830
mix the precious caterpillar fungus in here.

114
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:58,490
Your Majesty, don’t be angry!

115
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,870
I deserve to die.

116
00:09:00,110 --> 00:09:02,770
Who are you transporting out the medicines for?

117
00:09:05,950 --> 00:09:08,510
It’s Doctor Ye. Ye Tianshi!

118
00:09:12,150 --> 00:09:14,230
Go investigate the Imperial Hospital!

119
00:09:14,230 --> 00:09:15,960
I’ll see the so-called insects

120
00:09:16,590 --> 00:09:18,390
are people or ghosts!

121
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:22,170
Good fortunes for Your Highness!

122
00:09:22,230 --> 00:09:24,090
Good fortunes for Your Highness!

123
00:09:27,230 --> 00:09:28,110
This is?

124
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:29,630
This is a parrot Lord Syge

125
00:09:29,630 --> 00:09:31,750
brought for you for entertainment.

126
00:09:31,990 --> 00:09:33,390
It was trained for a long time

127
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:34,920
just to learn this one line.

128
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:38,870
This cousin of mine is always a yes-man.

129
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,990
He’s even worried the leaf from the tree

130
00:09:40,990 --> 00:09:42,920
would fall on his head and hurt him.

131
00:09:43,510 --> 00:09:44,870
Can’t believe such a person

132
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,830
has learned to kiss ass!

133
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,110
After the Silkworm Ceremony,

134
00:09:50,110 --> 00:09:51,550
your father's elder brother, Lord Rodo,

135
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:52,870
came to visit as well,

136
00:09:53,310 --> 00:09:55,510
hoping Your Highness can help him with promotion.

137
00:09:55,510 --> 00:09:57,110
This is all understandable.

138
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:02,190
This is from Prince He.

139
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:05,270
Prince He? How?

140
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:08,670
Such a precious parrot

141
00:10:08,990 --> 00:10:12,310
can only be afforded by the most knowledgeable bird expert,

142
00:10:12,310 --> 00:10:15,350
the most absurd prince

143
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:17,030
of the Asin Gioro clan

144
00:10:17,390 --> 00:10:20,110
Your Highness, if Prince He wanted to gift you,

145
00:10:20,270 --> 00:10:22,270
why wouldn’t he just give it to you directly?

146
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:22,950
Come.

147
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:26,030
Greetings to Your Highness the Empress.

148
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:26,750
What is it?

149
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:29,090
Your Highness,

150
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:31,150
Guard Suolun just brought a group of people,

151
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:33,880
angrily marching toward the Imperial Hospital.

152
00:10:33,950 --> 00:10:35,190
I was worried something might happen,

153
00:10:35,190 --> 00:10:36,670
so I rushed here to report.

154
00:10:37,630 --> 00:10:41,630
Imperial Guards are all young and strong with good control of the sword.

155
00:10:42,110 --> 00:10:43,910
If they frighten the Imperial Doctors,

156
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:46,310
who would dare to treat illness and save people in the future?

157
00:10:46,310 --> 00:10:47,840
Your Highness, so you mean…

158
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:51,150
You're the head eunuch of Imperial Household Department.

159
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,590
Whatever happen in the Forbidden City

160
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:54,120
should be at your disposal.

161
00:10:54,910 --> 00:10:56,510
I obey Your Highness' will.

162
00:10:57,550 --> 00:10:58,510
I take my leave.

163
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,610
Your Highness,

164
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:08,390
