167
00:11:11,550 --> 00:11:13,710
He's not someone I promoted after all.

168
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:16,230
I don’t quite trust him.

169
00:11:17,790 --> 00:11:19,230
Three bowls of water boiled down to half a bowl.

170
00:11:19,230 --> 00:11:21,070
Once a day, for half a month.

171
00:11:32,830 --> 00:11:33,870
Guard Suolun.

172
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:34,750
What…

173
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:36,110
What happened?

174
00:11:37,230 --> 00:11:37,670
Take him!

175
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:39,070
What? What’s going on?

176
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,270
What did I do?

177
00:11:40,470 --> 00:11:41,590
What are you doing?

178
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:45,150
We'll find out very soon whether you have committed a crime.

179
00:11:45,150 --> 00:11:45,710
