180
00:11:46,870 --> 00:11:47,630
Wait.

181
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,800
What are you searching for?

182
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:54,630
Officer Suolun,

183
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,870
what's going on?

184
00:12:04,550 --> 00:12:06,390
Those herbs are very precious. Don't touch them,

185
00:12:06,390 --> 00:12:06,990
Officer Suolun!

186
00:12:06,990 --> 00:12:08,470
We found one bunch of insect-damaged medicines in the backyard

187
00:12:08,470 --> 00:12:09,550
and nothing else.

188
00:12:10,470 --> 00:12:12,870
So it’s because of that bunch of medicines?

189
00:12:13,030 --> 00:12:13,960
Officer Suolun,

190
00:12:14,230 --> 00:12:16,350
those herbs were all damaged by insects.

191
00:12:16,350 --> 00:12:17,870
The people in the palace are all nobles,

192
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:19,870
Who would use those damaged medicines?

193
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:21,150
I had someone take them out

194
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:22,470
with good intention.

195
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:25,310
How did it become such a fuss?

196
00:12:27,710 --> 00:12:30,230
Doctor Ye, of course I trust you.

197
00:12:30,590 --> 00:12:32,070
But someone mixed in

198
00:12:32,070 --> 00:12:34,670
precious caterpillar fungus into it on purpose.

199
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:36,630
This is a theft of palace medicines.

200
00:12:36,630 --> 00:12:37,630
Not a small crime.

201
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:38,990
Caterpillar fungus?

202
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:41,390
Why didn't I see it?

203
00:12:41,750 --> 00:12:42,870
Well, officer Suolun!

204
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:43,830
Officer Suolun!

205
00:12:45,950 --> 00:12:47,230
Officer Suolun!

206
00:12:48,110 --> 00:12:49,040
Chamberlain Wu!

207
00:12:49,310 --> 00:12:50,150
What are you doing here?

208
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:53,150
Imperial Household Department is in charge of the palace matters.

209
00:12:53,150 --> 00:12:55,910
And the one who’s involved in the medicine transport was a eunuch.

210
00:12:55,910 --> 00:12:59,110
As the supervisor, I can't just turn a blind eye.

211
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:01,250
We've already searched here.

212
00:13:01,430 --> 00:13:02,950
You have searched,

213
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,710
but I haven't.

214
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:05,950
You mean,

215
00:13:06,190 --> 00:13:08,150
you don't trust Imperial Bodyguards?

216
00:13:08,150 --> 00:13:09,110
Oh, I don't dare.

217
00:13:09,710 --> 00:13:11,710
But Imperial Bodyguards and His Majesty

218
00:13:11,710 --> 00:13:14,630
mainly manage those upright matters,

219
00:13:15,150 --> 00:13:17,070
you won’t be able to figure out

220
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,390
the tricky things in the palace.

221
00:13:19,390 --> 00:13:20,190
Servants,

222
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:23,110
Search the entire place.

223
00:13:23,110 --> 00:13:25,510
Including the doctors’ office.

224
00:13:25,710 --> 00:13:27,630
Since precious medicines got out,

225
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,790
we need to examine the ledger

226
00:13:28,790 --> 00:13:30,030
with the medicines in and out in the last year.

227
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:32,590
Open your eyes and look closely.

228
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:34,630
No any penny should be missed! Hurry!

229
00:13:34,630 --> 00:13:35,470
Yes.

230
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:53,830
What is with the sighing?

231
00:13:55,590 --> 00:13:58,250
Since the incident at Palace of Eternal Spring,

232
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:01,110
His Majesty hasn't come to our Palace.

233
00:14:03,350 --> 00:14:04,350
It's all my fault.

234
00:14:05,110 --> 00:14:06,870
If I were too impulsive back then…

235
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:08,350
You were so decisive,

236
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:11,170
and now you changed your mind?

237
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:12,960
Of course I don't regret it,

238
00:14:13,510 --> 00:14:15,440
but I'm afraid you might regret it.

239
00:14:15,990 --> 00:14:18,390
In the past, no matter how busy His Majesty was,

240
00:14:18,390 --> 00:14:20,030
he'd come and see you.

241
00:14:21,150 --> 00:14:21,790
But now…

242
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:23,230
Since you can’t change it,

243
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:25,830
then don't regret over something that has happened.

244
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:26,830
Waste of time.

245
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:30,510
Yingluo.

246
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:33,590
Maybe you should apologize to His Majesty.

247
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:36,200
His Majesty is still angry with me.

248
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:37,950
If I go apologize now,

249
00:14:38,510 --> 00:14:39,270
I’ll be kicked out

250
00:14:39,270 --> 00:14:41,130
from Hall of Mental Cultivation.

251
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:43,830
