252
00:14:43,830 --> 00:14:45,110
But we can't just wait.

253
00:14:45,990 --> 00:14:47,050
I'm just not going.

254
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:49,790
If you really don't care,

255
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:52,170
then why did you draw the branch crooked?

256
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,630
I'm drawing a willow tree.

257
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:04,710
Unbelievable!

258
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:23,890
Take them away.

259
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:27,190
Your Majesty,

260
00:15:27,470 --> 00:15:28,950
I know your appetite isn't good,

261
00:15:28,950 --> 00:15:29,830
so

262
00:15:30,110 --> 00:15:32,670
all the dishes are cooked by vegetables.

263
00:15:33,590 --> 00:15:36,520
Like this mushroom stewed with cabbage, honey cake,

264
00:15:36,750 --> 00:15:39,910
fruit congee and Egg soup. All very mild.

265
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,750
Your Majesty.

266
00:15:45,510 --> 00:15:47,030
If you don’t like any of them,

267
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:48,350
try this preserved egg with candied mushroom.

268
00:15:48,350 --> 00:15:51,030
It’s tasty and tender.

269
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,110
Or,

270
00:15:52,230 --> 00:15:54,430
at least eat some fine noodles.

271
00:15:54,670 --> 00:15:56,750
Otherwise, I’ll be worried.

272
00:15:57,830 --> 00:16:00,830
The dishes were cooked by Zhang Dongguan, weren’t they?

273
00:16:00,830 --> 00:16:02,490
Your Majesty, did you forget?

274
00:16:02,710 --> 00:16:05,710
Zhang Dongguan was sent to Palace of Everlasting Joy.

275
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:12,270
No wonder I don’t like the dishes.

276
00:16:12,270 --> 00:16:13,590
Your Majesty is indeed right.

277
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:15,390
Chef Zhang’s Suzhou cuisine

278
00:16:15,510 --> 00:16:17,110
is top-notch!

279
00:16:17,710 --> 00:16:19,640
Especially that Suzhou meat dish.

