00:16:20,270 --> 00:16:23,190
That delicious broth and that lingering sweetness.

281
00:16:23,190 --> 00:16:24,990
No one is his match in the palace.

282
00:16:27,030 --> 00:16:29,950
Your Majesty, if you’d like,

283
00:16:30,510 --> 00:16:32,970
maybe we can go to Palace of Everlasting Joy?

284
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:36,990
Who said I am going to Palace of Everlasting Joy?

285
00:16:36,990 --> 00:16:39,510
