287
00:16:43,950 --> 00:16:45,750
And she doesn’t even feel sorry.

288
00:16:46,590 --> 00:16:47,590
A woman like her…

289
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:50,110
Your Majesty, please don’t be angry!

290
00:16:50,110 --> 00:16:53,030
So because Consort Ling is arrogant,

291
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:54,110
you shouldn’t leave

292
00:16:54,110 --> 00:16:56,030
Chef Zhang to her.

293
00:16:57,110 --> 00:16:59,110
