294
00:16:59,270 --> 00:17:01,150
we really don’t know how to serve her,

295
00:17:01,150 --> 00:17:03,410
so it’s hard for us to get Chef Zhang back.

296
00:17:05,470 --> 00:17:07,750
How dare you to slander Consort Ling?

297
00:17:08,750 --> 00:17:10,990
I deserve to die. Deserve to die.

298
00:17:14,470 --> 00:17:15,470
Your Majesty,

299
00:17:15,710 --> 00:17:19,589
