303
00:17:25,670 --> 00:17:26,750
Reporting to Your Majesty.

304
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,230
Her Highness the Empress says she has an urgent matter.

305
00:17:28,230 --> 00:17:30,350
She's asked you to come to Palace of Receiving Celestial Favor.

306
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:30,990
Well…

307
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:33,510
Wu Shulai,

308
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:37,030
tell everything you found out to His Majesty.

309
00:17:40,990 --> 00:17:41,670
Go on.

310
00:17:42,910 --> 00:17:46,190
I want to know as well

311
00:17:47,430 --> 00:17:49,390
how Imperial Hospital's embezzlement is linked to Consort Ling?

312
00:17:49,390 --> 00:17:50,190
Your Majesty,

313
00:17:50,390 --> 00:17:53,590
I checked through the medicine ledgers of the last whole year.

314
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:55,390
Ye Tianshi has been checking Consort Ling's

315
00:17:55,390 --> 00:17:56,510
wellness pulse all along.

316
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:58,750
And he's prescribed tonic to restore her body.

317
00:17:58,750 --> 00:17:59,630
I compared the ledger

318
00:17:59,630 --> 00:18:01,750
with the medicine used.

319
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:05,190
Not only ginseng and wolfberry were used in large amounts,

320
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:06,350
but also…

321
00:18:07,710 --> 00:18:08,710
Continue.

322
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:10,670
Consort Ling

323
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:14,650
has been taking contraception soup.

324
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:27,390
Your Majesty, Consort Ling receives royal favor.

325
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:29,630
She shouldn’t have done this in theory.

326
00:18:29,630 --> 00:18:30,710
I think

327
00:18:30,710 --> 00:18:32,040
she may have her reason.

328
00:18:32,990 --> 00:18:34,510
Your Majesty, don’t be angry.

329
00:18:34,510 --> 00:18:35,870
Let’s find out the truth.

330
00:18:35,870 --> 00:18:37,470
Don’t scare her.

331
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:01,510
Greetings to Your Majesty.

332
00:19:01,510 --> 00:19:02,040
Get lost!

333
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:11,870
Your Majesty.

334
00:19:12,030 --> 00:19:13,630
What’s really in the tonic

335
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:15,880
you’ve been taking?

336
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:22,350
Judging from your face,

337
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:25,730
you're acknowledging it.

338
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:29,510
Why?

339
00:19:43,110 --> 00:19:43,990
Your Majesty.

340
00:19:45,430 --> 00:19:46,390
About this…

341
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:49,310
I am asking. Why?

342
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:53,590
You won’t say?

343
00:19:55,950 --> 00:19:57,010
I’ll say it for you.

344
00:20:02,110 --> 00:20:04,110
Since you were at the Summer Palace,

345
00:20:04,990 --> 00:20:06,310
you’ve decided to

346
00:20:07,470 --> 00:20:09,070
get rid of Noble Consort Chun

347
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,470
to avenge Rongyin,

348
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:12,470
is that correct?

349
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:16,230
Yes.

350
00:20:16,390 --> 00:20:19,250
You tried your best to win Empress Dowager's favor,

351
00:20:20,430 --> 00:20:22,560
but actually you were targeting at me,

352
00:20:23,310 --> 00:20:24,310
right?

353
00:20:30,310 --> 00:20:31,190
Yes.

354
00:20:31,470 --> 00:20:32,800
You kept your distance,

355
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:35,160
but didn’t reject me entirely,

356
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:39,750
so that you could catch my full attention.

357
00:20:40,270 --> 00:20:40,950
No.

358
00:20:42,990 --> 00:20:44,850
You tried to clear your obstacles

359
00:20:45,630 --> 00:20:48,560
to earn the right to compete with Noble Consort Chun.

360
00:20:48,630 --> 00:20:49,560
Is that correct?

361
00:20:55,430 --> 00:20:56,270
Yes.

362
00:20:56,870 --> 00:20:58,190
As you wished.

363
00:21:00,350 --> 00:21:01,870
Su Jinghao is dead.

364
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:04,950
You don’t need to

365
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,430
use me anymore.

366
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:11,070
So you've gone cold completely.

367
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,790
Right?

368
00:21:15,670 --> 00:21:16,710
Say it!

369
00:21:17,430 --> 00:21:18,430
Is that correct?

370
00:21:23,870 --> 00:21:25,930
Since Your Majesty knows it already,

371
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:29,070
why bother ask?

372
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:31,910
I want to hear you say it personally.

373
00:21:39,630 --> 00:21:40,390
Yes.

374
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:45,150
Your Majesty is right.

375
00:21:49,910 --> 00:21:51,910
I wanted to avenge the late Empress,

376
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:55,950
so I became your consort.

377
00:21:58,310 --> 00:22:00,310
In order to ruin Noble Consort Chun,

378
00:22:02,030 --> 00:22:05,910
I did my best to win your heart.

379
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:11,790
Since I've taken my revenge now,

380
00:22:12,950 --> 00:22:14,630
Your Majesty

381
00:22:15,350 --> 00:22:17,310
holds no value to me anymore.

382
00:22:19,910 --> 00:22:22,230
I of course don't need to continue to fawn on you.

383
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:24,030
Since you don’t need me anymore,

384
00:22:25,590 --> 00:22:28,310
why did you make the mink fur hat for me?

385
00:22:30,430 --> 00:22:31,430
I feel guilty!

386
00:22:38,110 --> 00:22:39,230
What did you say?

387
00:22:42,910 --> 00:22:45,240
Because Your Majesty treated me too well,

388
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:47,230
so well that I felt guilty.

389
00:22:47,230 --> 00:22:50,030
But you still keep taking the contraception soup.

390
00:22:52,390 --> 00:22:53,710
Because I mean

391
00:22:56,990 --> 00:22:58,830
nothing to you.

392
00:23:00,710 --> 00:23:02,390
I’m just a pawn

393
00:23:02,950 --> 00:23:04,280
that’s been used by you.

394
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:08,080
Do you feel you are mistreated, Your Majesty?

395
00:23:09,670 --> 00:23:12,070
The late Empress was mistreated even more.

396
00:23:12,870 --> 00:23:13,710
Wei Yingluo.

397
00:23:15,190 --> 00:23:16,920
What do you want to say exactly?

398
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:26,470
Pain. Once it starts, it's forever.

399
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:29,550
Side by side, but unaware

400
00:23:32,910 --> 00:23:35,710
the parting of death that is grief above all grief.

401
00:23:36,710 --> 00:23:38,630
Compliance to lose yourself.

402
00:23:40,110 --> 00:23:43,150
Your Majesty personally made a poem of grief for her.

403
00:23:43,830 --> 00:23:47,070
The poem is so sincere and touching.

404
00:23:48,030 --> 00:23:49,470
The world will only know

405
00:23:49,910 --> 00:23:52,440
Your Majesty's devotion to the late Empress.

406
00:23:53,950 --> 00:23:55,430
But no one knows

407
00:23:56,990 --> 00:24:00,030
how she died.

408
00:24:00,030 --> 00:24:00,830
Stop talking!

409
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:02,630
Your Majesty has done it.

410
00:24:04,030 --> 00:24:05,630
Why don’t you dare to hear it?

411
00:24:06,790 --> 00:24:08,670
There are so many women in the world.

412
00:24:08,670 --> 00:24:10,910
Why did you favor Hitara Erqing?

413
00:24:11,990 --> 00:24:14,390
She was the late Empress's sister-in-law.

414
00:24:15,630 --> 00:24:16,830
New Year's Eve.

415
00:24:18,430 --> 00:24:21,960
Her Highness the Empress suffered the pain of losing her child,

416
00:24:22,430 --> 00:24:24,590
and received such grave humiliation.

417
00:24:26,310 --> 00:24:30,710
it was a situation that’s simply intolerable!

418
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:35,390
You finally spoke your true mind.

419
00:24:36,990 --> 00:24:38,720
Am I really a despicable person

420
00:24:39,270 --> 00:24:43,150
who takes advantage of his subject’s wife and forgets loyalty over a woman

421
00:24:43,150 --> 00:24:45,230
in your eyes?

422
00:24:49,910 --> 00:24:52,710
Your Majesty really doesn’t feel guilty about it?

423
00:24:55,070 --> 00:24:56,310
I don’t!

424
00:24:57,430 --> 00:24:58,590
Right or wrong,

425
00:24:59,790 --> 00:25:01,650
Your Majesty should know better.

426
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,600
When the Empress was alive,

427
00:25:26,510 --> 00:25:28,070
Your Majesty used her.

428
00:25:29,390 --> 00:25:30,910
After the Empress died,

429
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,950
you still wouldn't let her go.

430
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:38,440
Thirteenth year in Qianlong's reign.

431
00:25:39,710 --> 00:25:42,630
Imperial Hanlin Academy, Ministry of Rites and Imperial Clan Court

432
00:25:42,630 --> 00:25:44,390
all suffered heavy rebukes

433
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:46,870
over the late Empress' funeral.

434
00:25:48,470 --> 00:25:50,990
Fifty-three officials in

435
00:25:50,990 --> 00:25:53,390
Liangjiang, Fujian, Zhejiang, Hubei and Hunan

436
00:25:53,390 --> 00:25:56,030
were severely punished because they didn’t report

437
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:57,990
they came to the capital to attend the funeral.

438
00:25:57,990 --> 00:26:01,310
Many Eight Banners relatives in Shengjing, Ningxia and Hangzhou

439
00:26:01,310 --> 00:26:03,190
were punished by hair-shaving, death sentence or removing from their posts

440
00:26:03,190 --> 00:26:06,250
because they violated against the national mourning.

441
00:26:06,590 --> 00:26:08,990
Your Majesty went on a slaughter campaign.

442
00:26:09,230 --> 00:26:11,560
Other than your guilt toward the Empress,

443
00:26:12,790 --> 00:26:16,790
you really didn’t use it as a pretext to fulfill your political purpose?

444
00:26:17,670 --> 00:26:21,430
These words must have been hidden in your heart for so long.

445
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:22,190
Yes.

446
00:26:24,670 --> 00:26:27,150
I have always wanted to seek an answer from you

447
00:26:27,150 --> 00:26:28,430
for the late Empress.

448
00:26:30,830 --> 00:26:33,230
When I ascended to the throne,

449
00:26:35,510 --> 00:26:37,070
I obliged public sentiment

450
00:26:37,910 --> 00:26:39,310
and ruled with leniency,

451
00:26:40,510 --> 00:26:44,750
so as to pacify the wounds brought upon by the late Emperor's harshness,

452
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:48,910
make the officials content with their duties,

453
00:26:50,430 --> 00:26:53,110
and have people live a peaceful life.

454
00:26:54,910 --> 00:26:56,350
Thirteen years passed,

455
00:26:57,790 --> 00:27:00,790
the officials all get used to relying on my leniency,

456
00:27:02,590 --> 00:27:04,390
each and every holding sinecure

457
00:27:05,310 --> 00:27:06,840
and ignoring their duties.

458
00:27:09,310 --> 00:27:10,670
I needed a sword

459
00:27:12,630 --> 00:27:15,630
to show my authority and purge officialdom.

460
00:27:17,750 --> 00:27:19,110
And the late Empress

461
00:27:20,590 --> 00:27:22,030
was my sword.

462
00:27:24,190 --> 00:27:25,430
Your Majesty.

463
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:27,750
Fuca Rongyin lived

464
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:30,030
as Great Qing's Empress.

465
00:27:30,990 --> 00:27:32,270
Even in death,

466
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:35,950
I put her to her last use.

467
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:41,710
You are really too heartless.

468
00:27:41,910 --> 00:27:42,870
Wei Yingluo.

469
00:27:45,350 --> 00:27:47,030
I treated you so well

470
00:27:48,830 --> 00:27:50,890
that you forget one important matter

471
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:52,870
that I am an Emperor.

472
00:27:54,750 --> 00:27:56,610
Emperors are usually heartless.

473
00:27:58,670 --> 00:28:01,150
I can allow no one to challenge my authority.

474
00:28:02,990 --> 00:28:06,030
Since you entered the palace, you’ve belonged to me,

475
00:28:08,030 --> 00:28:09,830
no matter you are willing or not.

476
00:28:10,550 --> 00:28:12,880
You will be confined to the Forbidden City

477
00:28:13,550 --> 00:28:15,350
for your entire life.

478
00:28:17,270 --> 00:28:18,550
Until you get old.

479
00:28:20,230 --> 00:28:21,510
Until you are dead.

480
00:28:39,710 --> 00:28:40,550
By the way,

481
00:28:42,350 --> 00:28:43,280
You needn't take

482
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:45,610
the medicine anymore.

483
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:50,310
You won’t need it again.

484
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:12,230
Yingluo, Chamberlain Li just told me,

485
00:30:12,630 --> 00:30:14,230
there was medicine theft in the palace.

486
00:30:14,230 --> 00:30:16,230
Imperial Hospital was searched thoroughly.

487
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:17,890
Doctor Ye has been jailed too.

488
00:30:18,190 --> 00:30:19,470
Can you tell me

489
00:30:19,790 --> 00:30:21,190
what happened exactly?

490
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:26,720
What did you say?

491
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:29,590
His Majesty arrested Doctor Ye.

492
00:30:29,910 --> 00:30:32,570
He committed a mistake. Why is it related to you?

493
00:30:36,550 --> 00:30:38,950
Yingluo. Tell me!

494
00:30:42,030 --> 00:30:44,490
I have been taking contraceptive medicine.

495
00:30:45,910 --> 00:30:47,170
His Majesty found out.

496
00:30:49,870 --> 00:30:51,030
Are you crazy?

497
00:30:53,230 --> 00:30:54,870
All the consorts of the palace

498
00:30:54,870 --> 00:30:56,730
wish to give birth to a royal heir.

499
00:30:57,910 --> 00:30:59,510
Why are you still standing there?

500
00:30:59,510 --> 00:31:01,110
Go and beg His Majesty!

501
00:31:01,830 --> 00:31:03,360
Tell him you were confused.

502
00:31:03,470 --> 00:31:04,550
Tell him…

503
00:31:05,390 --> 00:31:07,190
I don’t know what you should say.

504
00:31:07,310 --> 00:31:09,040
But just go and beg His Majesty!

505
00:31:09,310 --> 00:31:10,110
Come on!

506
00:31:10,990 --> 00:31:11,590
Mingyu.

507
00:31:15,270 --> 00:31:16,070
It's too late.

508
00:31:16,430 --> 00:31:17,950
His Majesty favors you so much.

509
00:31:17,950 --> 00:31:19,230
It’s not too late.

510
00:31:19,590 --> 00:31:20,910
I told His Majesty

511
00:31:23,510 --> 00:31:24,590
about my revenge.

512
00:31:27,110 --> 00:31:27,910
Yingluo.

513
00:31:29,710 --> 00:31:31,590
How can you say such a thing?

514
00:31:34,710 --> 00:31:35,870
I couldn’t help.

515
00:31:38,230 --> 00:31:40,390
This is all you’ve got to say?

516
00:31:41,110 --> 00:31:43,170
I’ve always had a question in my head.

517
00:31:43,590 --> 00:31:45,110
I just wanted an answer.

518
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:47,640
Since I’ve opened my mouth,

519
00:31:47,950 --> 00:31:49,270
why not ask all the way?

520
00:31:49,590 --> 00:31:50,910
Now you're happy?

521
00:31:55,870 --> 00:32:00,110
Then, did His Majesty say how he will punish you?

522
00:32:17,110 --> 00:32:19,240
I think this Palace of Everlasting Joy

523
00:32:21,310 --> 00:32:24,350
will become a true cold palace from now on.

524
00:32:33,910 --> 00:32:34,790
Your Majesty.

525
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:37,350
I am very tired.

526
00:32:39,110 --> 00:32:40,590
I want to be alone.

527
00:32:42,310 --> 00:32:43,110
Yes.

528
00:33:21,670 --> 00:33:24,270
Your Majesty, why are you standing alone here?

529
00:33:25,710 --> 00:33:26,510
Empress.

530
00:33:41,590 --> 00:33:42,390
Empress.

531
00:33:44,910 --> 00:33:46,240
Have you ever blamed me?

532
00:33:46,590 --> 00:33:48,030
Why are you asking?

533
00:33:49,990 --> 00:33:51,430
Be honest to me.

534
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:56,750
I have.

535
00:34:03,910 --> 00:34:04,990
Then,

536
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,850
have you ever hated me?

537
00:34:10,389 --> 00:34:13,030
I’ve blamed you and complained about you,

538
00:34:13,350 --> 00:34:14,870
but I’ve never hated you.

539
00:34:23,350 --> 00:34:24,230
Why?

540
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:29,310
If Rongyin were still alive,

541
00:34:30,949 --> 00:34:32,590
she would hate me for sure.

542
00:34:32,989 --> 00:34:35,190
Your Majesty is the owner of Great Qing.

543
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:37,110
The Empress is the master of the Imperial Harem.

544
00:34:37,110 --> 00:34:39,710
Emperor and Empress are never a common couple.

545
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:42,070
If they spend all day indulged in

546
00:34:42,070 --> 00:34:43,790
sentiments and love,

547
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:46,239
it would court the laughter of others.

548
00:34:47,030 --> 00:34:48,489
Your Majesty, forgive me.

549
00:34:49,750 --> 00:34:51,679
I wasn't blaming the late Empress.

550
00:34:52,790 --> 00:34:55,590
It's just that everyone should have self-awareness.

551
00:34:55,590 --> 00:34:57,350
I received Your Majesty's grace

552
00:34:57,350 --> 00:34:59,430
and thus I must manage the family for you well.

553
00:34:59,430 --> 00:35:02,030
If not, I would be ashamed to see you.

554
00:35:02,590 --> 00:35:04,250
How could I blame or complain.

555
00:35:15,310 --> 00:35:16,550
But Consort Ling said

556
00:35:17,990 --> 00:35:20,830
that I’m ruthless.

557
00:35:23,390 --> 00:35:25,830
Your Majesty did nothing wrong

558
00:35:26,390 --> 00:35:29,110
with the country, the justice and the righteousness.

559
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:31,790
Your Majesty toils day and night to manage state affairs.

560
00:35:31,790 --> 00:35:34,470
You can't even manage to take care of your royal body.

561
00:35:34,470 --> 00:35:37,200
The establishment and the existence of the harem

562
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:40,680
are for taking care of Your Majesty and producing heirs.

563
00:35:40,750 --> 00:35:42,590
not bring troubles to you.

564
00:35:44,350 --> 00:35:47,070
Others say the palace is lonely.

565
00:35:48,270 --> 00:35:50,430
But does it mean one can do as they wish

566
00:35:50,590 --> 00:35:52,070
if leaving the palace?

567
00:35:54,070 --> 00:35:55,730
In every fields and industry,

568
00:35:55,870 --> 00:35:57,110
men are busy with work

569
00:35:57,710 --> 00:36:00,910
and women are busy with housework, working hard day and night.

570
00:36:00,910 --> 00:36:02,110
Compared to them,

571
00:36:02,390 --> 00:36:04,650
the consorts shouldn’t complain at all.

572
00:36:04,750 --> 00:36:06,750
The late Empress was the example to the harem,

573
00:36:06,750 --> 00:36:09,070
but she acted unfilial to her parents with her self-inflicted death.

574
00:36:09,070 --> 00:36:10,710
With all due respect,

575
00:36:11,550 --> 00:36:13,750
you owe nothing to Empress Xiaoxian.

576
00:36:14,430 --> 00:36:17,110
It was she who disappointed your trust.

577
00:36:25,590 --> 00:36:26,590
I know,

578
00:36:27,950 --> 00:36:28,870
Rongyin

579
00:36:30,990 --> 00:36:32,650
didn’t like to be restrained.

580
00:36:40,910 --> 00:36:42,040
Everybody longs for

581
00:36:42,750 --> 00:36:44,110
freedom.

582
00:36:44,550 --> 00:36:46,680
Your Majesty, you are the ruler of all,

583
00:36:46,870 --> 00:36:48,590
the one with most authority,

584
00:36:48,590 --> 00:36:50,520
but you don't have a day of freedom.

585
00:36:52,070 --> 00:36:54,710
Real freedom is paid with irresponsibility.

586
00:36:57,310 --> 00:37:00,470
Your Majesty, Consort Ling can hate you.

587
00:37:00,870 --> 00:37:02,530
Late Empress could blame you.

588
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:04,950
But I won’t.

589
00:37:12,110 --> 00:37:13,070
Even if

590
00:37:14,790 --> 00:37:16,550
I caused Lord Naerbu's death?

591
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:21,010
For my father's incident,

592
00:37:21,990 --> 00:37:23,750
I did blame you.

593
00:37:25,310 --> 00:37:27,570
But I felt so sorry after I calmed myself.

594
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:31,110
Even if everyone in the world hurts your feelings,

595
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:32,710
I am your Empress,

596
00:37:32,710 --> 00:37:33,950
I won’t hurt you.

597
00:37:35,390 --> 00:37:36,350
Otherwise,

598
00:37:36,470 --> 00:37:40,000
I would be no difference from the late Empress and Consort Ling.

599
00:37:44,870 --> 00:37:45,950
Empress.

600
00:37:47,790 --> 00:37:50,390
No one has ever said these words to me.

601
00:37:52,750 --> 00:37:53,790
You're the first.

602
00:37:59,110 --> 00:38:02,040
Your Majesty, even if everyone misunderstands you,

603
00:38:02,470 --> 00:38:04,390
I will always stand by your side.

604
00:38:05,230 --> 00:38:06,830
Understand and support you.

605
00:38:07,510 --> 00:38:09,310
You are the lofty son of heaven.

606
00:38:09,990 --> 00:38:13,110
No one has right to criticize you.

607
00:38:22,190 --> 00:38:23,190
Starting today,

608
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:25,710
you can all leave.

609
00:38:26,790 --> 00:38:28,110
Master, you…

610
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:30,150
Where do you want us to go?

611
00:38:30,910 --> 00:38:32,390
Go to Imperial Household Department

612
00:38:32,390 --> 00:38:34,990
and ask Chamberlain Wu to assign you new tasks.

613
00:38:36,270 --> 00:38:37,470
My palace

614
00:38:38,390 --> 00:38:40,190
will never need servants again.

615
00:38:40,870 --> 00:38:41,630
Master,

616
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:42,630
don’t say that.

617
00:38:43,070 --> 00:38:44,190
Such a big palace,

618
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:45,790
of course you need servants.

619
00:38:46,430 --> 00:38:47,710
From now on,

620
00:38:49,190 --> 00:38:51,120
His Majesty will never come again.

621
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:53,390
Don't doubt my words.

622
00:38:54,190 --> 00:38:55,390
My palace

623
00:38:55,950 --> 00:38:58,010
can’t offer you protection anymore.

624
00:38:59,230 --> 00:39:00,470
If you want to go,

625
00:39:01,470 --> 00:39:02,510
just leave now.

626
00:39:03,070 --> 00:39:03,670
Master.

627
00:39:03,870 --> 00:39:05,870
but every palace

628
00:39:06,030 --> 00:39:07,470
has a set number of servants.

629
00:39:07,470 --> 00:39:10,110
I’ve said that I don’t need them.

630
00:39:10,990 --> 00:39:11,950
None of them.

631
00:39:16,830 --> 00:39:18,760
If you don't leave, you will remain

632
00:39:18,870 --> 00:39:20,400
and suffer with the Master.

633
00:39:53,950 --> 00:39:54,870
Your Highness,

634
00:39:56,310 --> 00:39:59,040
I have the reputation of betraying my old Master.

635
00:39:59,510 --> 00:40:00,710
Where can I go?

636
00:40:01,470 --> 00:40:05,990
I think I’ll continue to serve you in the future.

637
00:40:17,790 --> 00:40:19,450
You are quite down-to-earth.

638
00:40:28,270 --> 00:40:29,070
Zhenzhu.

639
00:40:31,150 --> 00:40:31,910
You can go.

640
00:40:32,710 --> 00:40:33,470
No.

641
00:40:33,910 --> 00:40:35,910
I will stay with Sister Mingyu

642
00:40:36,350 --> 00:40:37,810
and continue to serve you.

643
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:39,990
There's laundry in the backyard.

644
00:40:39,990 --> 00:40:42,670
No one's here anymore. I will go and hang them up.

645
00:40:49,510 --> 00:40:50,910
I will go back to work too.

646
00:41:13,710 --> 00:41:15,190
You come with me.

647
00:41:22,390 --> 00:41:25,120
Your Highness the Empress, Consort Ling is here.

648
00:41:37,270 --> 00:41:39,530
Greetings to Your Highness the Empress.

649
00:41:41,430 --> 00:41:43,190
Consort Ling, how come you look

650
00:41:43,470 --> 00:41:45,710
so pale today?

651
00:41:45,710 --> 00:41:46,750
Your Highness,

652
00:41:47,030 --> 00:41:48,360
I’ll be straight to you.

653
00:41:49,030 --> 00:41:50,160
Everything has been

654
00:41:50,350 --> 00:41:52,110
under your control, right?

655
00:41:53,710 --> 00:41:55,440
Consort Ling is quite confused

656
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:57,550
to say such a peculiar thing.

657
00:41:58,790 --> 00:42:02,110
Did I ask you to take contraceptive soup?

658
00:42:03,470 --> 00:42:04,310
No.

659
00:42:04,310 --> 00:42:06,840
Did I ask you to fight with Noble Consort Chun?

660
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:07,710
No.

661
00:42:07,870 --> 00:42:09,990
Did I order you to kill Hitara Erqing?

662
00:42:09,990 --> 00:42:10,550
No.

663
00:42:11,310 --> 00:42:14,470
Everything was done willingly by me myself.

664
00:42:15,190 --> 00:42:16,190
This whole time,

665
00:42:16,630 --> 00:42:18,630
you’ve never asked me to do anything.

666
00:42:18,630 --> 00:42:20,190
You kept your hands clean

667
00:42:20,830 --> 00:42:24,030
and easily got rid of your sworn enemy Noble Consort Chun.

668
00:42:24,110 --> 00:42:26,870
In the end, you gave me the final blow.

669
00:42:28,150 --> 00:42:29,350
Consort Ling,

670
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:32,690
you are not sick. You've contracted hysteria instead.

671
00:42:33,470 --> 00:42:34,350
I am getting more confused

672
00:42:34,350 --> 00:42:36,430
by what you're saying.

673
00:42:41,590 --> 00:42:42,350
Him.

674
00:42:45,230 --> 00:42:48,910
Isn't he your most trusted supervisor?

675
00:42:49,110 --> 00:42:49,790
No.

676
00:42:50,470 --> 00:42:51,630
Starting today,

677
00:42:52,350 --> 00:42:55,790
he will be Your Highness' most loyal dog!

678
00:42:56,150 --> 00:42:59,150
Consort Ling. What do you mean?

679
00:42:59,430 --> 00:43:01,230
I should have known much earlier

680
00:43:01,670 --> 00:43:03,400
that it was just your first step

681
00:43:03,870 --> 00:43:05,350
to send Hupo to me,

682
00:43:06,110 --> 00:43:08,430
bringing about His Majesty's fury and suspicion.

683
00:43:08,430 --> 00:43:10,870
Then by taking advantage of the medicine theft case,

684
00:43:10,870 --> 00:43:13,590
you exposed that I have been taking contraceptive soup,

685
00:43:13,590 --> 00:43:16,320
and revealed the reason why I entered the palace.

686
00:43:16,430 --> 00:43:17,790
As proud as His Majesty,

687
00:43:18,190 --> 00:43:19,750
no matter how I explain,

688
00:43:19,910 --> 00:43:21,630
he wouldn’t forgive me whatsoever.

689
00:43:21,630 --> 00:43:23,110
But, how did Your Highness find out

690
00:43:23,110 --> 00:43:25,510
that I’ve been taking contraceptive soup.

691
00:43:30,750 --> 00:43:32,470
Unless you’ve put a spy

692
00:43:33,190 --> 00:43:34,590
by my side.

693
00:43:35,910 --> 00:43:36,710
Yingluo,

694
00:43:37,670 --> 00:43:39,230
you suspect I'm the spy?

695
00:43:39,230 --> 00:43:40,870
Only you

696
00:43:41,670 --> 00:43:43,150
and Doctor Ye knew

697
00:43:43,510 --> 00:43:45,310
that I took contraceptive soup.

698
00:43:45,670 --> 00:43:47,030
Mingyu is quick-tempered

699
00:43:47,030 --> 00:43:49,150
and I was afraid she couldn't keep the secret.

700
00:43:49,150 --> 00:43:50,950
So every time I took the medicine,

701
00:43:50,950 --> 00:43:52,510
I evaded her.

702
00:43:53,750 --> 00:43:56,310
Since the first day you entered Palace of Everlasting Joy,

703
00:43:56,310 --> 00:43:59,240
I’ve let you take care of everything with full trust.

704
00:43:59,910 --> 00:44:01,110
I never expected that

705
00:44:02,110 --> 00:44:03,790
this is how you’ve repaid me.

